❌ Critical Problems Found & Fixed
1. PORT binding — Program.cs
Root cause: Railway injects a dynamic PORT env-var. Without reading it, Kestrel listens on a port Railway never proxies, causing an immediate connection refusal.

Fix applied in Program.cs:

