await db.Database.MigrateAsync();
Wrapped in try/catch that re-throws so Railway's health check fails fast with a readable log instead of a silent hang.

7. UseHttpsRedirection() in production — Program.cs
Root cause: Railway terminates TLS at its edge proxy. The container only receives plain HTTP. Enabling HTTPS redirect inside the container causes an infinite redirect loop for all requests.

Fix:

csharp
if (!app.Environment.IsProduction())
{
    app.UseHttpsRedirection();
}
